title: MGS2 - Joe Biden Calls Raiden (Part 4 of 4)

media:group.media:title: MGS2 - Joe Biden Calls Raiden (Part 4 of 4)
media:group.media:description:
The FINAL codec conversation between Raiden and former Vice President Joe Biden from the 2001 video game Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty.

You can support this channel here: https://www.patreon.com/aamonhawk 

The song at the end of the video is "A Phantom Pain" from the MGSV OST by Ludvig Forssell
